# CivicConnect v3 — Accountability-Driven Architecture Update

## Core Vision Change

**Before**: Generic complaint board → issues go to "municipal" → get ignored  
**Now**: **Accountability system** → issues auto-assigned to HOD of specific department → deadline pressure → civilian gets HOD contact → resolution requires photo proof + verification

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A["👤 Citizen reports issue<br/>+ photo + GPS"] --> B["🤖 AI categorizes →<br/>Department + Criticality"]
    B --> C["📋 Issue assigned to<br/>Department HOD"]
    C --> D{"⏰ Deadline reached?"}
    D -->|No| E["HOD works on issue<br/>Civilian can contact HOD"]
    D -->|Yes| F["🔴 Auto-escalate to<br/>Supervisor"]
    E --> G["HOD uploads resolution<br/>photo + marks resolved"]
    G --> H["✅ Supervisor/Citizen<br/>verifies with tick"]
```

