## What's Changing

### 1. Database Schema Updates

#### Department — Add HOD info
```diff
model Department {
+  hodName     String?  @map("hod_name")
+  hodEmail    String?  @map("hod_email")
+  hodPhone    String?  @map("hod_phone")
+  hodTitle    String?  @map("hod_title")     // e.g. "Commissioner"
}
```

#### Issue — Add deadlines, resolution, urgency
```diff
model Issue {
+  deadline       DateTime?                  // auto-calculated based on criticality
+  urgencyScore   Int      @default(0)       // upvotes + category weight
+  assignedToId   String?  @map("assigned_to")
+  resolutionPhoto String? @map("resolution_photo")
+  resolutionNote  String? @map("resolution_note")
+  verifiedBy      String? @map("verified_by")  // supervisor/citizen who verified
+  verifiedAt      DateTime? @map("verified_at")
+  escalated       Boolean @default(false)
}
```

#### User — Add department assignment for municipal users
```diff
model User {
-  role String @default("citizen")
+  role         String  @default("citizen")  // citizen | municipal | supervisor | ngo
+  departmentId Int?    @map("department_id") // only for municipal users
}
```

